15 sale, assignment, change in the dealer's executive management,
16 principal operator, or appointment of a designated successor,
17 to inquire about or consider whether another manufacturer or
18 distributor had previously denied, rejected, or otherwise turned
19 down the application of the applicant, or any person or entity
20 affiliated with the applicant, to acquire a franchise or
21 dealership or become principal operator, part of the executive
22 management, or a successor owner or manager of a dealership.
