5 CLARIFY DEFINITION OF MOTOR VEHICLE DEALER
6 SECTION 4. G.S. 20-286(11) reads as rewritten:
7 "(11) Motor vehicle dealer or dealer. –
8 a. A person who does any of the following:
9 …
10 6. For commission, money, or other thing of value, or on behalf
11 of another person sharing ten percent (10%) or more common
12 ownership, offers new vehicles as part of a subscription
13 program. This sub-sub-subdivision shall not apply to any
14 person providing a vehicle subscription or monthly rental
15 program on or after January 1, 2025.
16 7. Performs any warranty service or recall work on motor
17 vehicles; provided, however, that this sub-sub-subdivision
18 shall not be applicable with respect to a commercial fleet
19 customer that has a designation as such by the manufacturer or
20 distributor.
21 …."
